<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2023-11-22T14:01:33-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2023-11-22T14:01:33-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-22T14:01:33-05:00</updated><title>福特缩减了密歇根州的电动汽车电池工厂计划</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;F-150 Lightning 正面的福特标志&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/lkF78tk2ouw4ezDZzMUrDKzJPsA=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox- cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72892990/ahawkins_220504_5202_0010.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;全电动 F-150 Lightning 的特写。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Andrew Hawkins / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;czzFLD&quot;>;福特宣布，由于客户购买电动汽车的需求降温以及劳动力成本上升，它将削减即将建成的电动汽车电池工厂的产能。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://media.ford.com/content/fordmedia/fna/us/en/news/2023/11/21/blue-oval-battery-park-michigan-update.html&quot;>;汽车制造商表示&lt;/a>;将把原来建造密歇根工厂的 35 亿美元计划投资减少到 20 亿美元左右，现在预计只雇用 1,700 名工人，而不是 2,500 名。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;F39rAq&quot;>;福特&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/2/11/23595909/ford-battery-plant-michigan-evs&quot;>;最初宣布&lt;/a>;于二月份合作建设雄心勃勃的密歇根电池工厂与中国宁德时代新能源科技有限公司（CATL）合作，该公司生产 LFP（磷酸铁锂）电池。该工厂现在每年仅生产约 20 吉瓦时的电池，产量减少约 43%。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;bcP7Sg&quot;>;为了让电动汽车有资格获得高达 &lt;a href=&quot; https://www.theverge.com/2023/4/20/23691597/ev-tax-credit-eligible-vehicles-battery-irs-china&quot;>;7,500 美元...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p >; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/22/23972680/ford-michigan-ev-battery-plant-reduction-plans&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/22/23972680/ford-michigan-ev-battery-plant-reduction-plans" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/22/23972680/ford-michigan-ev-battery-plant-reduction-plans</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-22T13:59:32-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-22T13:59:32-05:00</updated><title> Max、Paramount Plus、Hulu 等平台的最佳黑色星期五流媒体优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;绿色和白色背景上的 Hulu 徽标插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/3j-f3ef4ipJwlDcnjluNSqJnvu0=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72891666/acastro_STK061_hulu_04.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;一年支持广告的 Hulu 现在不到 12 美元。&lt;/em>; |插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge &lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Up5UhG&quot;>;如果感觉像每个流媒体服务&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23901586/streaming-service -prices-netflix-disney-hulu-peacock-max&quot;>;今年价格上涨&lt;/a>;，可能是因为大多数都涨价了。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/18/23922319/netflix-q3-earnings-2023-price-hike-increase-basic-premium&quot;>;Netflix&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/25/23931577/apple-tv-plus-news-arcade-one-subscription-price-increase&quot;>;Apple TV Plus&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/3/23901448/discovery-plus-price-increase-monthly-cost&quot;>;Discovery Plus&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https:// /www.theverge.com/2023/8/9/23826500/disney-plus-hulu-no-ads-plan-price-increases&quot;>;Disney Plus&lt;/a>; 只是最近的几个例子，但仍有方法以应对价格上涨。毕竟，黑色星期五带来了各种各样的优惠，包括节省每月流媒体账单的方法。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;VJkz6i&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;您现在可以购买的最佳早期黑色星期五科技优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23899698/best-early-black-friday- tech-deals-amazon-target-best-buy-walmart-sale&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 2023 年节日礼物指南&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23939057/holiday -gift-guide-2023-best-ideas-unique-tech-gadgets&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;7hzi4e&quot;>;事实上，一些流媒体服务正在提供抵消了最近价格上涨的交易——至少暂时是这样。例如，Paramount Plus 可能&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/5/22/23733505/paramount-plus-showtime-price-increase&quot;>;将其最便宜计划的价格提高到每月 5.99 美元&lt;/a>;，但目前起价仅为 1.99 美元。更好的是，新订阅者和回访订阅者都有资格享受这笔交易，这是真正的罕见......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23965708/black- friday-2023-streaming-deals-max-paramount-plus-hulu-cyber-monday&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23965708/black-friday-2023-streaming-deals-max-paramount-plus-hulu-cyber-monday" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23965708/black-friday-2023-streaming-deals-max-paramount-plus-hulu-cyber-monday</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-22T13:32:30-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-22T13:32:30-05:00</updated><title>黑色星期五 100 美元以下最佳优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一只手举起 Kindle Paperwhite&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/VRNp93gtsOhpHG4GX23T2Lf60DQ=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/72892831/cgartenberg_211020_4803_0003.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Kindle Paperwhite 是一款很受欢迎的礼物，当您购买几乎相同的儿童友好型号时，它的价格不到 100 美元。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chaim Gartenberg / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Xpmerm&quot;>;这是一年中最美好的时光？噗，更像是最贵的。礼物、旅行、装饰品、聚会、美味佳肴……所有这些加起来可以让你的钱包省不少钱。这就是为什么我们努力以各种方式帮助您节省费用，从 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23951136/gifts-under-100-best-cheap-tech-ideas-2023-budget &quot;>;针对&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21587765/black-friday-cyber-monday-best-deals-how-to-find&quot;>;产品制定经济实惠的礼品指南&lt;/a>;寻找交易的技巧&lt;/a>;。现在，我们在下面汇总了 100 美元以下的最佳黑色星期五优惠 — 其中许多是 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23939057/holiday-gift-guide-2023-best-ideas -unique-tech-gadgets&quot;>;我们的礼品指南中的特色内容&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;k8loXn&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 最喜欢的 50 美元以下节日礼物&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23952179/tech-gifts-under-50-best-cheap-ideas -2023-budget&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 最喜欢的 25 美元以下节日礼物&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23874403/tech-gifts-under-25-best-cheap -ideas-stocking-stuffers-2023-budget&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;zqcCCP&quot;>;我们发现了一系列打折的小玩意和商品，可用于很棒的礼物，来自 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Lavender-Bloom-bundle-TP-Link-Smart/dp/B0CL8HJ3HD?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; 目标=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Echo Pop&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Fitbit-Exercise-Equipment-6-Months-Membership/dp/B0CC62ZG1M?tag=theverge02-20&quot; 相关=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Fitbit Charge 6&lt;/a>; 到 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Fujifilm-Instax-Mini-Instant-Camera/dp/B0BWP15J1P? tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Fujifilm Instax Mini 12&lt;/a>; 甚至一对 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Apple-AirPods -Charging-Latest-Model/dp/B07PXGQC1Q?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot; Sponsored nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;AirPods&lt;/a>;。不过，还有一些优惠可以帮助您节省其他费用，例如换色 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CCYSDP2V?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener “ target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;节日智能灯串...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23965961/black-friday-2023-tech -deals-under-100-cyber-monday&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23965961/black-friday-2023-tech-deals-under-100-cyber-monday" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23965961/black-friday-2023-tech-deals-under-100-cyber-monday</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-22T12:47:52-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-22T12:47:52-05:00</updated><title> WiiM Amp 是一款具有 Mac Mini 风格的流媒体接收器</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;从四分之三角度拍摄的 WiiM 放大器图片。它是灰色的，形状大致像 Mac Mini，右前方有一个大旋钮，中间有一个播放按钮。左侧一条深灰色的铅笔粗线几乎延伸到左角。该线左端上方有一个紫色电源 LED，在其右侧上方，有 6 个圆形 LED 用来指示音量——左边 4 个是亮起来，最右边的稍微变暗。另外两个是黑暗的。” src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/yVVW1Nt7qaPgSnDh6XOC1fBOiio=/160x0:1890x1153/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72892652/WiiM_Amp___Lifestyle_4.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;售价 299 美元的 WiiM Amp 具有无源立体声扬声器输出和大量流媒体支持。&lt;/em>; |图片：Linkplay Technology&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;wTvSp7&quot;>;Linkplay Technology 今天宣布了其产品阵容的新成员：&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CGCLXH4H ?th=1&amp;amp;tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;WiiM 放大器&lt;/a>;。这款售价 299 美元的设备作为接收器具有明显的复古焦点，甚至比 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/8/23822610/wiim-pro-plus-streamer-multiroom -audio-streaming-release-date&quot;>;WiiM Pro Plus&lt;/a>;，该公司于今年早些时候推出，得益于物理输出，可以让您直接输出到一组老式无源立体声扬声器。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;10DvDX&quot;>;WiiM Amp 现在是该公司最昂贵的流媒体盒，但它有可能为合适的人赢得它。得益于丰富的流媒体标准支持以及适合自带扬声器人群的独特输出集，它比大多数紧凑型 AirPlay 2 接收器更加通用。这可能只占人口的一小部分，但像这样的无线接收器并不多……&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/ 11/22/23972352/wiim-amp-airplay-2-chromecast-wireless-receiver-vintage-hi-fi&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/22/23972352/wiim-amp-airplay-2-chromecast-wireless-receiver-vintage-hi-fi" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/22/23972352/wiim-amp-airplay-2-chromecast-wireless-receiver-vintage-hi-fi</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-22T12:46:27-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-22T12:46:27-05:00</updated><title>阅读 Microsoft 关于 OpenAI 混乱的内部备忘录</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;OpenAI - Microsoft&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/x5mAdEgf1QxEMWyb5xGIPQqlhWk=/2x0:3724x2481/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/ image/72892648/1795954328.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Berke Bayur/Anadolu via Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;iQAX2J&quot;>;周三凌晨，OpenAI 宣布 &lt; a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/22/23967223/sam-altman-returns-ceo-open-ai&quot;>;Sam Altman 将重新担任首席执行官&lt;/a>;，继 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23965982/openai-ceo-sam-altman-fired&quot;>;星期五发生冲击波&lt;/a>;。周末，看起来像 Altman 和 OpenAI 联合创始人 Greg Brockman &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/20/23968829/microsoft-hires-sam-altman-greg-brockman-员工-openai&quot;>;可能最终会加入微软&lt;/a>;，领导一个新的人工智能研究实验室。但经过几天的谈判，情况不再如此，OpenAI 任命了新的董事会，并重新任命 Altman 为公司首席执行官。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;0BGIF3&quot;>;经过一个周末的混乱场景，包括&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/20/23968988/openai-employees-resignation-letter-microsoft-sam-altman&quot;>;数百名 OpenAI 员工威胁&lt;/a>;辞职并加入微软后，事情似乎就安定下来了。微软首席技术官兼 AI 执行副总裁凯文·斯科特 (Kevin Scott) 现在向微软员工讲述了 OpenAI 的动荡。这是首次在全公司范围内向 Microsoft 员工传达有关...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/22/23972572/microsoft-internal-memo -kevin-scott-openai&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/22/23972572/microsoft-internal-memo-kevin-scott-openai" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/22/23972572/microsoft-internal-memo-kevin-scott-openai</id><author><name>汤姆·沃伦</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-22T12:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-22T12:00:00-05:00</updated><title>宫崎骏很有说服力</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;吉卜力工作室电影《男孩与苍鹭》中的静态图像。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/g1U5le2dbrpv2bVgC13h-GUzunA=/182x0:1739x1038/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72892346/HERON_img_7.5.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;男孩和苍鹭。&lt;/em>; |图片来源：GKIDS&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;当《男孩与苍鹭》导演打来电话时，长期担任《新世纪福音战士》动画师的本田武士已经签约参与另一部电影的制作。本田说：“当宫崎骏对你这么说时，真的没有办法拒绝。”&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23971512/boy-and-the-苍鹭武本田采访新世纪福音战士&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23971512/boy-and-the-heron-takeshi-honda-interview-evangelion" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23971512/boy-and-the-heron-takeshi-honda-interview-evangelion</id><author><name>安德鲁·韦伯斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-22T11:41:18-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-22T11:41:18-05:00</updated><title>柯达新款Super 8胶片相机真的要来了</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;柯达新款 Super 8 相机。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/gRLCTtxWbsjnG82y1BnSqf6iwig=/1x0:1324x882/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72892252/Super_8_Detailed_Render_Black.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;柯达新款 Super 8 相机。&lt;/em>; |图片：柯达&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;xCXWrr&quot;>;柯达正准备实际销售其早在 CES 2016 上宣布的 Super 8 胶片相机。它更新了 &lt;a href=&quot;https:/ /www.kodak.com/en/motion/page/super-8-camera?CID=go&amp;amp;idhbx=super8camera&amp;amp;ref=404media.co&quot;>;相机产品页面&lt;/a>;，带有新的“注册购买”按钮以允许潜在客户注册他们的兴趣。柯达电影全球董事总经理 Vanessa Bendetti 告诉 The Verge，该公司预计该相机将于 12 月 4 日在美国限量发售，然后在加拿大、英国和美国发售。其他欧洲市场。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;0Uq7SX&quot;>;这款相机上市销售时售价高达 5,495 美元。当你考虑到这一点时，这不仅仅是昂贵的，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.404media.co/new-kodak-super-8-film-video-camera-thought-to-be-vaporware-is-actually- come-out-costs-5-495-charges-with-microusb/&quot;>;正如 &lt;em>;404 Media&lt;/em>; 所说&lt;/a>;，老式 Super 8 相机通常只需几百美元 - 它也是与柯达之前宣布的相比昂贵......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/22/23972513/kodak-super-8-film-camera-lcd -screen-price-release-date-specs-features&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/22/23972513